C_{nm}(z)=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}u_{n}^{*}(x,z)\, u_{m}^{*}(y,z)\, E(\vec{r})\, e^{ikz}\mathrm{\, d}x\mathrm{d}y\label{eq:coef-campo-gaussiano}\end{equation}

